snippet.title: Amber Alert | -Z_Torcher Zion- (Dubstep)
snippet.description:
I made this a couple of weeks back. I initially had the idea when I heard an Amber Alert on my TV, talking about a Flash Flood Warning. 

Soo, with creative juices running through my head, I sampled the first Alert Test that happened about a decade ago and mixed it in as a Dubstep beat. (Also, I guess Sirenhead)

Hope you guys enjoy this new beat, and as always

Stay 🔥FLAMIN'🔥 Guys! 
PEACE!✌👌
#Dubstep #AmberAlert #Siren #Sirenhead #Music #Banger #Warning
